'''Tasenbert n teɣdemt tagreɣlant''' (S [[Taglizit|Tegnizt]]: ''International Court of Justice'', s [[asegzel (tutlayt)|usegzel]]: '''ICJ''') akken i tettwassen s yisem n '''Tasenbert tamadlant'''<ref>{{amnir n web|anrggar1=Koh|amexwar1=Steven Arrigg|azwel=4 Things You Should Know About The Hague|akala=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/steven-arrigg-koh/4-things-you-should-know-_1_b_5725138.html|azmez n tuwwṭa=17 meɣres 2017| akala n ufaylu = https://web.archive.org/web/20171011002720/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/steven-arrigg-koh/4-things-you-should-know-_1_b_5725138.html | azmez n ufaylu = 11 tuber 2017 }}</ref>. D tasudut taɣedmant tagejdant n tuddsa n [[Tuddsa n Yeɣlanen Yeddukklen|Yeɣlanen Yeddukklen]].<ref>[http://www.icj-cij.org/documents/index.php?p1=4&p2=2&p3=0 Statute of the International Court of Justice]. Retrieved 31 August 2007. {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171230061331/http://www.icj-cij.org/documents/index.php?p1=4&p2=2&p3=0 |date=30 dujamber 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=William|first1=Samore,|title=National Origins v. Impartial Decisions: A Study of World Court Holdings|journal=Chicago-Kent Law Review|date=1956|volume=34|issue=3|pages=193–222|url= http://scholarship.kentlaw.iit.edu/cklawreview/vol34/iss3/1|accessdate=6 June 2016|issn=0009-3599|akala n ufaylu= https://web.archive.org/web/20171011002429/http://scholarship.kentlaw.iit.edu/cklawreview/vol34/iss3/1/|azmez ufaylu=2017-10-11}}</ref><ref>{{amnir n web|akala=http://www.un.org/en/sections/un-charter/chapter-xiv/index.html|azwel=Chapter XIV|tansa=www.un.org|tutlayt=en|azmez n tuwwṭa=2017-11-03| akala n ufaylu = https://web.archive.org/web/20180725083309/http://www.un.org/en/sections/un-charter/chapter-xiv/index.html | azmez n ufaylu = 25 yulyu 2018 }}</ref>, Asutel-is yezga-d di [[Den Haag|Lahay]] ([[Timura n Wadda|Hollanda]]). Dɣa tga d anagraw amyiwen seg 6 n inagrawen n Yeɣlanen Yeddukklen ur nelli ara di [[New York]]. Tennulfa-d deg useggas n [[1945]] tebda imahilen-is deg useggas n [[1946]] dɣa teṭṭef adeg n [[Tasenbert Tameɣlalt n Teɣdemt Tagreɣlant|Tsenbert Tameɣlalt n Teɣdemt Tagreɣlant]].<ref>{{amnir n web
| akala = http://www.diplomatie.gouv.fr/ar/politique-etrangere-de-la-france/la-justice-internationale/la-cpi/
