| akala n ufaylu = https://web.archive.org/web/20171006043958/http://www.diplomatie.gouv.fr:80/ar/politique-etrangere-de-la-france/la-justice-internationale/la-cpi | azmez n ufaylu = 6 tuber 2017 }}</ref>. I tamawt yessefk ad tili tukza (ameyyez) gar Tesenbert n teɣdemt tagreɣlant d [[Tasenbert Tiniɣit Tagreɣlant|Tsenbert Tiniɣit Tagreɣlant]] 

Tesenbert n teɣdemt tagreɣlant d tin ilan (yesɛan) armud aɣedman meqqren. Tbeṭṭu s unect n izarafen [[Asaduf agreɣlan|usaduf agreɣlan]]  deg imennuɣen iɣedmen i d-yettilin gar n tmura

Taɣdemt-a tessuddes seg 15 n [[Amzarfu|yimzurfa]] i ferren-iten [[Agraw amatu n yeɣlanen yeddukklen|wegraw amatu n yeɣlanen yeddukklen]] d [[Aseqqamu n Tɣellist n Yeɣlanen Yeddukklen|useqqamu n Tɣellist]] i tenzagt (lmudda) n 9 n iseggasen. Akken i yezmer ad yili wallus (aɛawed) n wefran n yigmamen. ⅓ n yigmamen ttwafranen yal 3 n iseggasen akken i yegdel ad ilin sin n yimzurfa yezdin deg yiwet n [[taɣlent|teɣlent]]. Ma deg tegnit n tmekkast (Lmut) n umzarfu ad yili wefran n umzarfu niden yettadamen taɣlent n umzarfu yukkesen (yemmuten) i wakken ad yeṭṭef adeg-is alamma tfukk tenzagt-is

